Kim Kardashian and husband Kanye West are in the capital Yerevan on an eight-day visit to the country of her dad's birth  . 
  The couple are staying at the Armenia Marriott Hotel in the Armenian capital on Republic Square . 
  The pair are visiting the country for the first time with their daughter North and sister Khloe . 
  The visit comes as the country marks the 100th anniversary of the Armenian Genocide  . 
  The Kardashian family are staying in the city and are staying with their sister in the same hotel  . 
  The family are in Armenia for the visit of their late father Robert Kardashian . 
 